dashboard/       â†’ Dashboard-specific components
portfolio/       â†’ Portfolio management components
markets/         â†’ Market data & trading view components
watchlist/       â†’ Watchlist features
alerts/          â†’ Price alert components
charts/          â†’ All chart/visualization components

ğŸ“ HOOKS:
- useCryptoData     â†’ Fetch & cache crypto prices
- usePortfolio      â†’ Portfolio state management
- useWatchlist      â†’ Watchlist CRUD operations
- useAlerts         â†’ Alert management
- useLocalStorage   â†’ Persist data to localStorage
- useDebounce       â†’ Debounce search inputs
- useInfiniteScroll â†’ Load more data on scroll
- useWebSocket      â†’ Real-time price updates (optional)

ğŸ“ SERVICES:
- coinGecko.js      â†’ API calls to CoinGecko
- endpoints.js      â†’ API endpoint constants
- axios.config.js   â†’ Axios instance with interceptors
- toast.js          â†’ Notification system

ğŸ“ UTILS:
- formatters.js     â†’ formatCurrency(), formatPercent(), formatDate()
- calculations.js   â†’ calculateROI(), calculateTotal(), getProfitLoss()
- validators.js     â†’ validateAmount(), validateCoinId()
- constants.js      â†’ API_BASE_URL, CACHE_TIME, etc.

ğŸ“ CONTEXT:
- PortfolioContext  â†’ Global portfolio state (holdings, total value)
- ThemeContext      â†’ Dark/light mode toggle
- WatchlistContext  â†’ Global watchlist state

