DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOW
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

1. Start with: npm create vite@latest crypto-portfolio-tracker -- --template react
2. Install dependencies: npm install
3. Add Tailwind: npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
4. Add libraries: npm install axios recharts lucide-react react-router-dom
5. Create folder structure above
6. Build components from common â†’ complex
7. Implement API service layer
8. Connect pages with routing
9. Add state management (Context API or Zustand)
10. Polish UI/UX with animations

